00:14:41.435 --> 00:14:41.900
LAURA MURPHY: Oh,
that's awesome.

00:14:41.900 --> 00:14:43.160
BEN FOLDS: It's really good.

00:14:43.160 --> 00:14:43.430
That's what--

00:14:43.430 --> 00:14:44.360
LAURA MURPHY: That's
what this poster is?

00:14:44.360 --> 00:14:44.570
BEN FOLDS: That's what that is.

00:14:44.570 --> 00:14:45.620
LAURA MURPHY: Is her name Lisa?

00:14:45.620 --> 00:14:45.980
BEN FOLDS: No, no.

